Contran Corp: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback















contran corp
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Specialty Finance
Sub-Industry: Other Financial Services
Contran Corp. is a holding company that owns stakes in various companies. The Company's holdings include companies that produce chemicals, metals, waste management, computer support systems, precision ball bearing slides, fencing, and wire products.




